{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::30973779271::vessel::25a65220-d0f4-11f0-9f04-db7ad29040b7","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: West Mediterranean -Riviera / Corsica / Sardinia\n\nSbronzo is a refined catamaran, thoughtfully designed to deliver maximum comfort in every area on board. The four spacious cabins, each with a private bathroom, accommodate up to eight guests in an intimate and well-appointed setting, while the skipper has access to a fifth cabin with dedicated facilities.\n\nThe exterior areas are the true highlight of this catamaran: the flybridge, complete with a large sunbathing area and comfortable seating, is perfect for relaxing while taking in the panoramic views. The bow and aft dinettes provide welcoming spaces for socializing at any time of day. Notably, the aft table seats up to 10 guests, making it ideal for open-air lunches and dinners.\n\nThe generous aft swim platforms allow for direct access to the sea, offering an authentic experience in close contact with the water and the surrounding marine life.","blueprint":{"name":"SBRONZO","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::25a65220-d0f4-11f0-9f04-db7ad29040b7::assets::fd368c50-d0f9-11f0-a3d3-213bec07d556/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::25a65220-d0f4-11f0-9f04-db7ad29040b7::assets::fd57a8e0-d0f9-11f0-a3d3-213bec07d556/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::25a65220-d0f4-11f0-9f04-db7ad29040b7::assets::fd352cc0-d0f9-11f0-a3d3-213bec07d556/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::25a65220-d0f4-11f0-9f04-db7ad29040b7::assets::fd32bbc0-d0f9-11f0-a3d3-213bec07d556/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::25a65220-d0f4-11f0-9f04-db7ad29040b7::assets::fd31f870-d0f9-11f0-a3d3-213bec07d556/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::25a65220-d0f4-11f0-9f04-db7ad29040b7::assets::fd310e10-d0f9-11f0-a3d3-213bec07d556/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::25a65220-d0f4-11f0-9f04-db7ad29040b7::assets::fd3